{"tid":954483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長太醜被渣男退婚！單親媽淚崩「花3年整形」翻轉人生","createTime":"2018-12-24T15:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T02:35:46.000Z","uid":212399,"like":20,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e531036b2be4cf04e9b9d3dbdf48d8346b0473c4","tid":954483,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T15:37:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3786/d3786956.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3786%2Fd3786956.jpg&h=92f4adad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Huyen曾因長太醜，被男友家人嫌棄。（圖／翻攝Huyền Nguyễn Nguyễn臉書）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n越南胡志明一名28歲的單親媽媽Huyen分享自己整型前的遭遇，表示過去因為皮膚黑又單眼皮，不斷遭到周圍的人嘲笑，連婚姻都被男友的家人反對，即使生下了孩子，還是被退婚，這才讓她下定決心整形，擁抱新的人生。<br />\n綜合外媒報導，Huyen表示，她過去因為長得不好看，常被周圍的人貶低、辱罵，最後更是遭到男友家人反對，只好帶著孩子默默結束這段感情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3786/d3786959.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3786%2Fd3786959.jpg&h=4bd4bf01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Huyen3年內花了13萬元整形，讓自己變更好。（圖／翻攝Huyền Nguyễn Nguyễn臉書）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3786/d3786957.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3786%2Fd3786957.jpg&h=5e5ead33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n她說，因為助理的工作，她只能先將女兒寄放在媽媽那，每到周末才能去探視對方一次；期間，她也不斷存錢整形，3年下來約花費1憶越南盾（約13萬元新台幣），「由於經濟不好，我在整形後也沒休息多久就開始工作，在隆乳後的第3天便忍著疼痛去上班，這是讓我感到最痛苦的時間。」<br />\nHuyen表示，她的媽媽因擔心健康問題，起初不接受也不同意她去整形，「在母親看到我的改變後，她也逐漸贊同我」，甚至她與以前的朋友見面後，對方也會大為吃驚。<br />\nHuyen認為，她完全不後悔整形，因為術後她更有自信，在面對工作也取得了一定的成就，目前也對自己的外表很滿意，但在存一筆錢會將鼻子再稍微維修一下。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3786/d3786958.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3786%2Fd3786958.jpg&h=877ebf9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181224/1339393.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181224%2F1339393.htm&d=T5NaEXNrdDpnUjFX2ZNWyp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=bf7b5476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181224/1339393.htm</a>"},{"pid":"51b12fa54a417772aaed8a4ceecb34e402a90b4e","tid":954483,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T15:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea9b6625e5428b21b1a1d66a3c71bcfd10af7ad","tid":954483,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T15:44:37.000Z","msg":"13萬整完賣唔賣到5萬"},{"pid":"9afab5255fc5a3a9cc09ceb4c875cb34df96b772","tid":954483,"uid":87757,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T15:46:57.000Z","msg":"整得幾好"},{"pid":"a663db13e605c3749e6ceef1d4d86ce26de129b0","tid":954483,"uid":38904,"like":51,"dislike":3,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T15:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/transform/20151012/aNYB-fxirmpy1515629.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftransform%2F20151012%2FaNYB-fxirmpy1515629.jpg&h=f1e37079&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"468d91002754e22f4a2bcb5cbbd0574ce065b30a","tid":954483,"uid":49197,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T15:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/15288614859253450ffb2ef\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp1.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2Fpgc-image%2F15288614859253450ffb2ef&h=74964b5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6ca80769488866fd1eaa84a6d4ae76ac434a289","tid":954483,"uid":52824,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"a663db13e605c3749e6ceef1d4d86ce26de129b0","tid":954483,"uid":38904,"like":51,"dislike":3,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T15:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/transform/20151012/aNYB-fxirmpy1515629.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftransform%2F20151012%2FaNYB-fxirmpy1515629.jpg&h=f1e37079